{"tid":2344546,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個親身遇到邪教嘅經歷","createTime":"2020-12-28T21:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T16:50:40.000Z","uid":117718,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"811e471f9083d158cb21d87113f8e2392b781774","tid":2344546,"uid":117718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T21:51:16.000Z","msg":"訓唔著嚟開下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n前年自己一條友去台北玩，去得旅行習慣點都搵啲廟/神社之類嚟拜下，體驗下唔同事物、求個姻緣都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後去到一間樓上舖嘅姻緣廟，裡面都有大佛壇位擺設、燒香、抽籤等等有文有路正正常常<br />\n仲可以擲下聖筊，佢地係要求擲到中聖筊為止先會有下一個流程，擲咗四五次中咗，佢地廟祝班人就好興奮咁話我同個佛有緣，話有啲人係一日內擲極都擲唔到，證明同個佛冇緣要下次再嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我已經：<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />wtf？！<br />\n<br />\n啲廟祝都好親切成日撩人傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />身為外國嚟嘅朋友當然要同啲本地人吹下水，吹吹下佢地仲留埋我一齊係度食飯盒，話當識多個朋友<br />\n<br />\n食飯吹水嘅時候傾到香港嘅事，佢地都係啲典型嘅外國人不過不失嘅反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到目前為止都正正常常<br />\n<br />\n之後講到啲人示威受傷嗰part，佢地就覆我一句：如果佢地都識得神功護體就好了。<br />\n我當堂內心打咗個突，金庸小說啊？神功護體？！<br />\n而且佢地成班超級認真咁討論呢個神功護體，咁嘅氣氛我又唔可以當聽唔到轉話題，只好問下佢地真係有神功護體呢樣嘢？<br />\n佢地就拍曬心口話有，佢地所有廟祝兄弟姐妹都修煉過，大家都有神功護體，去示威去遊行完全唔怕！<br />\n仲逐個同我介紹啊邊個邊個有咩技能，啊邊個邊個擅長咩咩咩（但我太過震驚完全聽唔入腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽完我即刻覺得此地不宜久留<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喇喇聲食完個飯就閃咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔敢再去嗰度附近"},{"pid":"56f81853925d3df9229bcfe5270b27ce48d1071c","tid":2344546,"uid":16685,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T22:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fvmwSAg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfvmwSAg.jpg&h=1bb07a25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n試下隊佢一刀睇下堅唔堅"},{"pid":"566feb58cf74b008d871e179f13c2b9aac7d7b31","tid":2344546,"uid":8833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T23:01:28.000Z","msg":"你錯失左一場天下之間最大嘅機緣<br />\n我諗我知邊間<br />\n因為我都去過<br />\n<br />\n利申：刀槍不入"},{"pid":"bfbe622fdd31b43c7b7801ce3517f56af1474b87","tid":2344546,"uid":55874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"56f81853925d3df9229bcfe5270b27ce48d1071c","tid":2344546,"uid":16685,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T22:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fvmwSAg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfvmwSAg.jpg&h=1bb07a25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n試下隊佢一刀睇下堅唔堅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T23:02:37.000Z","msg":"個信念一鬆嘅時候阿群就攞住把嘢入咗"},{"pid":"3255ce527c0a875589b5601890df0110918e2336","tid":2344546,"uid":16685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bfbe622fdd31b43c7b7801ce3517f56af1474b87","tid":2344546,"uid":55874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"56f81853925d3df9229bcfe5270b27ce48d1071c","tid":2344546,"uid":16685,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T22:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fvmwSAg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfvmwSAg.jpg&h=1bb07a25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n試下隊佢一刀睇下堅唔堅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T23:02:37.000Z","msg":"個信念一鬆嘅時候阿群就攞住把嘢入咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T23:06:19.000Z","msg":"就係因為條橫丫腸突然發炎一痛"},{"pid":"362b20f84ae810581d7eb2ee20b2763091f5c6ec","tid":2344546,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T23:09:04.000Z","msg":"神功最怕橫丫腸"},{"pid":"732176a4c0ae69b10ccb81f95328451b2c9e66e5","tid":2344546,"uid":108477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:48:07.000Z","msg":"笑死"},{"pid":"973010bdc8b67947fe40bd79455551579b099768","tid":2344546,"uid":379538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01